# =============================================================================
# Telegram Job Aggregator — Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
# Copy to .env (for local dev) or set in Vercel project settings.
# All AI provider keys stay SERVER-SIDE — they're only used by /api/extract.
# =============================================================================

# ---- AI Providers (ALL OPTIONAL — app works without any of these) ----
#
# ZERO-COST MODE (default):
#   If no AI key is set, the app uses a built-in rule-based extractor that
#   parses Telegram messages with regex + heuristics. Less accurate than an
#   LLM but 100% free and works offline. Good enough for basic use.
#
# To enable AI-powered extraction (better quality), set ONE of these keys:
#
#   DeepSeek — $5.50 free credit (~37K requests). Get key at:
#     https://platform.deepseek.com
#
#   Mistral — free tier, rate-limited but no daily cap. Get key at:
#     https://console.mistral.ai
#
#   OpenRouter — works globally but free tier limited to 50 req/day:
#     https://openrouter.ai
#
# UNCOMMENT ONE OF THESE TO ENABLE AI EXTRACTION (otherwise rule-based is used):
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
# DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=...
# MISTRAL_MODEL=mistral-small-latest
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=nvidia/nemotron-3-nano-30b-a3b:free
# KIMI_API_KEY=...
# OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_MODEL=phi4:latest

# ---- App config ----
NODE_ENV=development
